homebridge for home

Docker image is at (now Private)
https://cloud.docker.com/repository/docker/isharma/homebridge-smartthings-docker

Running the container:

sudo docker run --rm -d -p 8000:8000 -p 51826:51826 --name homebridge isharma/homebridge-smartthings-docker:latest

Resources:

https://homebridge.io/
https://github.com/nfarina/homebridge
https://www.npmjs.com/package/homebridge-smartthings
